'''EGS-zs8-1'''是在北天的[[牧夫座|牧夫座]]方向上發現的一個[[紅移#河外星系觀測|高紅移]]的[[萊曼斷裂星系|萊曼斷裂星系]]<ref name=paper>{{cite journal |authors=Oesch, P.A. et al. |title=A Spectroscopic Redshift Measurement for a Luminous Lyman Break Galaxy at z=7.730 using Keck/MOSFIRE |url=http://arxiv.org/abs/1502.05399 |date=3 May 2015 |journal=[[ArXiv|ArXiv]] |arxiv=1502.05399 |accessdate=6 May 2015 |bibcode=2015arXiv150205399O |archive-date=2015-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107080314/http://arxiv.org/abs/1502.05399 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2015年5月，EGS-zs8-1是已知的所有[[星系|星系]]中[[光譜|光譜]][[紅移|紅移]]最高的，意味著它是觀測到最遙遠和最古老的星系<ref name="HB-20150505">{{cite web |last1=Villard |first1=Ray |last2=Chou |first2=Felicia |title=Astronomers Set a New Galaxy Distance Record |url=http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/archive/releases/2015/22/full/ |date=5 May 2015 |work=[[HubbleSite|HubbleSite]] |accessdate=7 May 2015 |archive-date=2016-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160913033106/http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/archive/releases/2015/22/full/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="AP" />。但在2015年7月，EGS-zs8-1最遙遠和最古老的地位被[[EGSY8p7|EGSY-2008532660]]超越<ref name=DailyMail-2015-07-16>{{cite news |url= http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-3164703/A-galaxy-far-far-away-Astronomers-confirm-star-13-1-billion-light-years-away-distant-known-universe.html |title= A galaxy that rally IS far, far away: Astronomers confirm star system 13.1 billion light-years away is the most distant known in the universe |author= Jonathan O'Callaghan and Ellie Zolfagharifard |date= 16 July 2015 |publisher= Daily Mail (London) |accessdate= 2015-10-14 |archive-date= 2016-03-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215009/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-3164703/A-galaxy-far-far-away-Astronomers-confirm-star-13-1-billion-light-years-away-distant-known-universe.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

== 述述 ==
測量EGS-zs8-1的紅移[[哈伯定律#紅移速度|Z]]=7.73，對應於[[距離測量_(宇宙學)#光程|光程]]（light travel distance）約為130億4000萬光年的距離，也就是130億4000萬的地球年齡。這個星系顯示高效率的[[恆星形成|恆星形成]]，所以它釋放的[[電磁波譜|電磁波譜]]峰值在[[紫外線#子分類|真空紫外線]]
的部分，波長接近{{convert|121.567|nm|Å|abbr=on}}的[[來曼系|萊曼α發射譜線]]，這是由於強烈的輻射來自新誕生的高溫[[恆星分類#歷史|藍星]]，因此它被歸類為[[萊曼斷裂星系|萊曼斷裂星系]]；高紅移的[[星暴星系|星暴星系]]輻射出萊曼α發射線。由於[[宇宙學紅移|宇宙學紅移]][[都卜勒效應|都卜勒效應]]造成[[測度膨脹空間|測度膨脹空間]]（metric expansion of space）使來自星系的峰值光譜已經[[紅移|紅移]]至[[紅外線|紅外線]]的<ref name=paper />。星系的[[同移距離|同移距離]]（光旅行距離乘以[[哈伯常數|哈伯常數]]，引起度量空間的擴張）已經距離地球約300億光年<ref name="NYT">{{cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |authorlink=Dennis Overbye |title=Astronomers Measure Distance to Farthest Galaxy Yet |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/06/science/astronomers-measure-distance-to-farthest-galaxy-yet.html |date=5 May 2015 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=6 May 2015 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906045708/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/06/science/astronomers-measure-distance-to-farthest-galaxy-yet.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

EGS-zs8-1約誕生於[[大爆炸|大爆炸]]後的6億7,000萬年，當時正是[[再電離|再電離]]期間。這個星系被發現在宇宙還很年輕的時期，就比當時在附近的其它鄰居巨大<ref name="AP">{{cite news |last=Borenstein |first=Seth |title=Astronomers find farthest galaxy: 13.1 billion light-years |url=http://apnews.excite.com/article/20150505/us-sci--farthest_galaxy-46c792535a.html |date=5 May 2015 |publisher=[[AP_News|AP News]] |accessdate=6 May 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304000051/http://apnews.excite.com/article/20150505/us-sci--farthest_galaxy-46c792535a.html |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。依據它輻射的光亮估計，它當時的質量已經是[[銀河系|銀河系]]目前質量的15%。這個星系製造新恆星的速率大約是銀河系目前速率的80倍，或是相當於每年800{{Solar mass|link=y}}的恆星質量<ref name="NYT" />。抵達地球的光是來自EGS-zs8-1的恆星，而當時那些恆星的年齡是在1億至3一歲之間<ref name="SP-20150505">{{cite web |last=Cofield |first=Calla |title=This Galaxy Far, Far Away Is the Farthest One Yet Found |url=http://www.space.com/29319-farthest-galaxy-ever-found.html |date=5 May 2015 |work=[[Space.com|Space.com]] |accessdate=7 May 2015 |archive-date=2015-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002063401/http://www.space.com/29319-farthest-galaxy-ever-found.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。EGS-zs8-1的年齡使其是處於[[再電離|再電離]]階段創造出來的，當時在星系之外的氫是在中性與電離之間變換著的階段。根據該星系發現者的說法，EGS-zs8-1和其它早期的星系可能是造成再電離的原因<ref name=Phys>{{cite web |author=Staff |title=Astronomers unveil the farthest galaxy |url=http://phys.org/news/2015-05-astronomers-unveil-farthest-galaxy.html |publisher=[[Phys.org|Phys.org]] |accessdate=6 May 2015 |date=5 May 2015 |archive-date=2017-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911142756/https://phys.org/news/2015-05-astronomers-unveil-farthest-galaxy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Farthest Galaxy Spotted Yet Is 13 Billion Light-Years Away|url = http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/05/150506-most-distant-galaxy-astronomy-space|website = National Geographic News|accessdate = 2015-06-18|first = Michael D.|last = Lemonick|first2 = National Geographic PUBLISHED May|last2 = 06|archive-date = 2015-07-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150703004713/http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/05/150506-most-distant-galaxy-astronomy-space/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 發現 ==
在2013年，[[耶魯大學|耶魯]]的天文學家Pascal Oesch在審視[[哈伯太空望遠鏡|哈伯太空望遠鏡]]的影像時發現一個異於平常的光點。他使用[[史匹哲太空望遠鏡|史匹哲太空望遠鏡]]確認了這個物體的存在<ref name=AP />。使用位於[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]的[[凱克望遠鏡|凱克望遠鏡]]的多目標遠紅外線光譜儀（[[MOSFIRE|MOSFIRE]]）探測，計算該天體的[[紅移|紅移]]，然後進行精確的星系年齡測量<ref name="Phys"/>。Oesch和她在耶魯的夥伴與[[聖塔克魯茲加利福尼亞大學|加利福尼亞大學聖塔克魯茲分校]]宣布了此一發現，將它命名為EGS-zs8-1，在2015年5月超越舊有的紀錄約3,000萬年，成為迄今最古老和最遙遠的星系<ref name=AP />。

